caption.title: Model fit was quantified by calculating the relative likelihood of observing the data within the simulations.
caption.p: A higher likelihood is represented by a hotter color. From left to right: Base model, Exhaustion of Susceptibles (ES), Lack of Access to Care (LAC), Anti-Retroviral Therapy usage (ART), ES and LAC, ES and ART, LAC and ART, and ES, LAC, and ART. Details provided in S2 File.
